Description: he intimacy and splendor of the outdoor heated pool at TI is an essential element of any Las Vegas vacation.The double chaise lounges, plush round ottomans, live DJ* and 25 person hot tub provide the finest amenities for socializing with friends over tropical frozen infusions, tasty bites, or simply enjoying some gratifying solo time basking in the sun.
Location: 3300 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109
